# PartyKit Multiplayer Server
# For local dev: leave empty to use default (localhost:1999)
# For production: set to your deployed PartyKit URL
VITE_PARTYKIT_HOST=ndg-multiplayer.partykit.dev

# Claude NPC refinement (SERVER-ONLY - set these in the Vercel project env, not in this file).
# Never prefix the key with VITE_: any VITE_* var is inlined into the client bundle and
# shipped to every browser. The server reads process.env.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in api/_lib/claude-refine.ts.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
#
# Refinement stays OFF unless this is exactly "true". Do not enable without the cost controls
# and input hardening in docs/current/11-eternal-stream-and-security-hardening.md.
# ENABLE_CLAUDE_REFINEMENT=false
#
# Optional Claude model override for refinement (defaults to a Sonnet model in code).
# CLAUDE_MODEL=
